SIMPLE: telephoto_lens
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Telephoto lens
<hw>Tel`e*pho"to lens</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a special compound camera
lens with a long effective focal length but used in a camera with a
short focal length, allowing large images to be obtained of distant
objects when used in a camera in place of an ordinary lens; -- called
also <altname>telephotographic lens</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Telepolariscope</ent>⟦br⟧
